snippet.title: Zet Zillions | Date Reveal Trailer - Coming to Steam on May 23rd!
snippet.description:
Your journey through the galaxy is about to start, commander trash! 

Zet Zillions is coming to Steam on May 23rd! Watch our new trailer and play the NEW DEMO during the Steam Deckbuilders Fest, from March 25th to April 2nd. 

Thanks to Baarlord, Jorbs and Techsmith314 for being part of this new trailer!

Wishlist now: https://2link.in/DAPjm
